---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Academia Europa"
  description="Academia Europa is a European postgraduate professional education institution for experienced practitioners. Discover our mission, philosophy, and long-term institutional vision."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="About"
    title="A European Institution for Postgraduate Professional Education."
    lede="Academia Europa was created for professionals who have moved beyond the beginning of their careers and now seek structure, depth, and direction."
  />

  <Section eyebrow="Who We Are" title="An institution, not a marketplace.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa is a European postgraduate professional education institution dedicated to structured, evidence-based learning for experienced practitioners. We are not a university, and we do not award state-recognised degrees. We are an institution of professional education — a place where expert-led teaching, scientific discipline, and professional identity meet.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Why We Exist" title="Continuing education, reimagined as progression." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Across the professions, continuing education has become an inventory of isolated hours. It does not produce progression, and it rarely produces mastery. Academia Europa exists to change that — to architect a serious, long-term educational ecosystem where experienced professionals can move with clarity from competence to authority.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Identity" title="A European institution with an international outlook.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Rooted in Portugal and shaped by European academic values, Academia Europa serves a global community of practitioners. Our programmes are designed to travel — across countries, languages, and professional traditions — while preserving the discipline of European postgraduate education.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Long-Term Vision" title="A multi-disciplinary professional institute." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa begins with veterinary medicine through Veterinary Academy International, and will, over time, extend into other professional fields including medicine, dentistry, pharmacy, law, technology, and leadership.</p>
      <p>Each future academy will be developed in collaboration with qualified educators and institutional partners in that field.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Operating Entity">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa is operated by <strong class="text-navy-deep font-medium">Solex Education Unipessoal LDA</strong>, registered in Portugal.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Base>
